negotiator.analysis
Class Analysis

java.lang.Object
  negotiator.analysis.Analysis

public class Analysis
extends java.lang.Object

This class calculates the following characteristics of the negotiation space: - Pareto-efficient frontier; - Nash product optimal outcome; - Kalai-Smorodinsky optimal outcome.

Author:
